---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — IdeaVault" description="How IdeaVault finds startup ideas using AI.">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-primary">About IdeaVault</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-1">
        AI-powered startup idea discovery, updated daily.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-text-primary">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-1">How it works</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Every day, IdeaVault scans 8 sources for demand signals — Reddit, Hacker News,
          Product Hunt, GitHub Trending, Dev.to, Lobste.rs, NewsAPI, and Google Trends.
          A two-stage AI pipeline classifies each signal, then produces a structured idea
          brief with market sizing, competitors, build complexity, and a confidence score.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-1">The pipeline</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1">
          <li>Scrape 600+ signals daily from 8 sources</li>
          <li>Pre-filter by engagement (top ~65 signals)</li>
          <li>Stage 1: Classify with AI — pass or skip</li>
          <li>Stage 2: Full analysis — idea brief with market data</li>
          <li>Deduplicate and store in the database</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-1">What you get</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1">
          <li>Structured idea briefs with TAM/SAM/SOM market sizing</li>
          <li>Competitor analysis with specific named competitors</li>
          <li>Build complexity and timeline estimates</li>
          <li>Monetization angle with pricing suggestions</li>
          <li>Confidence score (0-100) based on signal strength</li>
          <li>Source links back to the original discussion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-bold mb-1">Built with</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Python pipeline on Linux, Claude API for analysis, Cloudflare Workers + D1 for
          the API, Astro + React for the frontend. All deployed on Cloudflare's edge network.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/" class="text-accent hover:underline text-sm">
        ← Browse ideas
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
